-- Chrysler to offer zero percent financing for 72 months
-- 
-- Fri Jul 25, 2008 3:20pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/07/25/us-chrysler-incentives-idUSN2543082320080725

 

 DETROIT  (Reuters) - Chrysler LLC will offer zero percent financing for up to 72 months on some of its key larger vehicles such as the Dodge Aspen and the Jeep Grand Cherokee and Commander, a dealer contacted by phone said on Friday. 

 Chrysler also is offering "pretty profound" rebates of up to $5,000 on some of its vehicles, the dealer said. (Reporting by  David Bailey  and  Poornima Gupta )